Package: ghapp
Title: GitHub App Token Generation
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Ian", "Flores Siaca", email = "iflores.siaca@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Generate installation access tokens for GitHub Apps. Supports
    environment variables for CI/CD, GitHub Enterprise Server, scoped permissions,
    token caching, and multiple installations.
